Module Simulator

Package kin.dyn

This package contains dynamic components of the robot's model.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Controllable
    An interface for all controllable components such as ServoComponent or LinearMotorComponent.
    FixSidePart
    Marker interface for components that is in the body direction.
    Identifiable  
    TailSidePart
    Marker interface for components that is counter-body direction.
    Touchable
    An interface for all components that contain TouchPoint objects.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Body
    A dynamic body component.
    Component
    The abstract upper class of all dynamic components.
    ConnectionPoint
    A ConnectionPoint mounts a component to a greater part, e.g. a leg to body.
    LinearMotorComponent
    A dynamic linear motor component.
    Segment
    A dynamic segment component.
    ServoComponent
    A dynamic servo component.
    TConnector
    A dynamic T-connector component.
    TerminationPoint
    A dynamic termination point component.
    TouchPoint
    A dynamic touchpoint component.
    TouchSegment
    A dynamic touch segment component.
